Subject: [PATCH] Emit alias-scope noalias metadata in vectorize_codegen

---
 .../link/numba/dispatch/_llvmlite_self_ref.py | 66 ++++++++++++++++
 .../link/numba/dispatch/vectorize_codegen.py  | 76 ++++++++++++++++---
 2 files changed, 131 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)
